title: Synchronous Generators by ION BOLDEA
description:
ISBN: 084935725X
Title: Synchronous Generators (Electric Power Engineering Series)
Author: Ion Boldea
Publisher: CRC
Publication Date: 2005-11-09
Number Of Pages: 448

Part of the two-volume Electric Generators Handbook, Synchronous Generators provides a comprehensive reference for the topologies, modeling, control, design, and testing of standard and emerging synchronous generator systems. The first three chapters provide the general background material, including basic performance equations and practical dynamic models and transfer functions. The rest of the book focuses on the many facets of synchronous generators and is dedicated to electric machine
